{"tid":621231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［關愛座hunter現身？］鄉音男拒讓關愛座 車內同肥男打架","createTime":"2018-04-08T06:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T07:08:47.000Z","uid":89134,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48cf302c8069d886d6b9f2691aee045d0ef847f5","tid":621231,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"凌晨近零時，一輛由小西灣開往黃大仙的九巴106號線隧道巴士，在銅鑼灣告士打道景隆街站上落客時，一名肥身材姓林(40歲)男子與妻子、嬰兒及母親上車。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n當時巴士並未客滿，下層仍有座位，而車內右方兩個關愛座，靠窗位置坐有一名手抱嬰兒的女士，另一靠走廊座位坐有一名戴眼鏡姓吳(33歲)男子。肥男走前要求他讓座給老人家，但該名操內地口音的男子拒絕，雙方發生爭執。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n據同樣在景隆街站上車的乘客王小姐稱，兩人以粗言互駡，繼而動手扭作一團，歷時約1分鐘，其後被乘客制止，據稱是新移民的鄉音男被打到流鼻血，眼鏡打歪。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n當時九巴駛至告士打道上橋位，車長報警並停車等候，但有乘客趕火車要求車長開車，最後車長開車過紅隧，在康莊道巴士站才停車，等候警察到來。警方接報到場，兩人分別鼻傷及頭痛不適送院，同涉打架被捕。<br />\r\n<br />\r<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180408/58046246\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F58046246&d=IHyLF%2BKTKc3wSGV5mAMi0C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=ecff86a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F58046246&h=47a07981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180408/58046246</a>"},{"pid":"769ad4c121fd50fa07d7714f377be258252f93de","tid":621231,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/150530_5cbb6a2fe60abee802e0f3bc12cdc7bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F150530_5cbb6a2fe60abee802e0f3bc12cdc7bb.png&h=e89f9e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07233944b992d3024f3abf6eb2350d991e30f915","tid":621231,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"去完政總返屋企"},{"pid":"285aff453524d915f60f160bb23bc89c15862751","tid":621231,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07233944b992d3024f3abf6eb2350d991e30f915","tid":621231,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:06:38.000Z","msg":"去完政總返屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"去小西灣食宵野"}]}